Placeholder so //go:embed dist always succeeds.

The real vendor artifacts (jassub.js, jassub-worker.js, the wasm,
default.woff2, LICENSE, version.txt) are written here by ../gen.go
and gitignored — present in dist/ only after running

	go run web/jassub/gen.go

When this directory holds nothing but Readme, jassub.Handler
returns 404 and jassub.Path returns "". The player view branches
on an empty Path and stays on the WebVTT downconversion path.
